   Actor Gary Coleman has bought a home in a Denver
subdivision with a view of the Front Range Mountains.
   Coleman, 20, star of the now-defunct ``Diff'rent Strokes,'' is
moving from Chicago into the $470,000 home in Highlands Ranch,
publicist Skip Heinecke said Friday.
   ``He doesn't ski,'' Heinecke said. ``But he likes to drive
off-road'' and owns a couple of Jeeps. Coleman also likes to ride
horses, he added.
