to Japan _ along with lighting, costumes and other paraphernalia _
in two Boeing 747s later this month.
   The only member of the menagerie to miss the flight will be
Gilda, a 40-year-old elephant that disappears in each show. The
3{-ton pachyderm will go by boat.
